Class CompletionEvent<T extends Event<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jgrapes.core.internal.EventBase<T>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Future<T>, Associator, Eligible
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    KeyValueStoreData, NioRegistration.Completed, Request.Completed, Started

    public abstract class CompletionEvent<T extends Event<?>>
extends Event<T>

    A base class for completion events that use the completed event as their result type. Use event() to access the completed event while handling the completion event.
